<h1 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-size: 36px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Modules</h1>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Modules are self-contained software units that consist of<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-models.html">models</a>,<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-views.html">views</a>,<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-controllers.html">controllers</a>, and other supporting components. End users can access the controllers of a module when it is installed in<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-applications.html">application</a>. For these reasons, modules are often viewed as mini-applications. Modules differ from<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-applications.html">applications</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>in that modules cannot be deployed alone and must reside within applications.</p>
<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 30px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Creating Modules<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="creating-modules"></a></h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">A module is organized as a directory which is called the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html#$basePath-detail">base path</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>of the module. Within the directory, there are sub-directories, such as<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">controllers</code>,<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">models</code>,<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">views</code>, which hold controllers, models, views, and other code, just like in an application. The following example shows the content within a module:</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">forum/
    Module.php                   the module class file
    controllers/                 containing controller class files
        DefaultController.php    the default controller class file
    models/                      containing model class files
    views/                       containing controller view and layout files
        layouts/                 containing layout view files
        default/                 containing view files for DefaultController
            index.php            the index view file
</code></pre>
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Module Classes<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="module-classes"></a></h3>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Each module should have a module class which extends from<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html">yii\base\Module</a>. The class should be located directly under the module's<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html#$basePath-detail">base path</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>and should be<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-autoloading.html">autoloadable</a>. When a module is being accessed, a single instance of the corresponding module class will be created. Like<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-applications.html">application instances</a>, module instances are used to share data and components for code within modules.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">The following is an example how a module class may look like:</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">namespace&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">app</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">modules</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">forum</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">;<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />class&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">Module&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">extends&nbsp;\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">yii</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">base</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">Module<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">{<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">init</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">()<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">parent</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">::</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">init</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">();<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$this</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">-&gt;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">params</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'foo'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">]&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'bar'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">;<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;...&nbsp;&nbsp;other&nbsp;initialization&nbsp;code&nbsp;...<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">}<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />}</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">If the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">init()</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>method contains a lot of code initializing the module's properties, you may also save them in terms of a<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-configurations.html">configuration</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>and load it with the following code in<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">init()</code>:</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">public&nbsp;function&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">init</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">()<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />{<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">parent</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">::</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">init</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">();<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;initialize&nbsp;the&nbsp;module&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;configuration&nbsp;loaded&nbsp;from&nbsp;config.php<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">Yii</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">::</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">configure</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">(</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$this</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,&nbsp;require(</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">__DIR__&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">.&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'/config.php'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">));<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />}</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">where the configuration file<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">config.php</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>may contain the following content, similar to that in an<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-applications.html#application-configurations">application configuration</a>.</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">&lt;?php<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">return&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'components'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;list&nbsp;of&nbsp;component&nbsp;configurations<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'params'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;list&nbsp;of&nbsp;parameters<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />];</span></code></pre>
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Controllers in Modules<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="controllers-in-modules"></a></h3>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">When creating controllers in a module, a convention is to put the controller classes under the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">controllers</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>sub-namespace of the namespace of the module class. This also means the controller class files should be put in the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">controllers</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>directory within the module's<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html#$basePath-detail">base path</a>. For example, to create a<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">post</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>controller in the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">forum</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>module shown in the last subsection, you should declare the controller class like the following:</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">namespace&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">app</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">modules</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">forum</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">controllers</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">;<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />use&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">yii</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">web</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">Controller</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">;<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />class&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">PostController&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">extends&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">Controller<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">{<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;...<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">}</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">You may customize the namespace of controller classes by configuring the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html#$controllerNamespace-detail">yii\base\Module::$controllerNamespace</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property. In case when some of the controllers are out of this namespace, you may make them accessible by configuring the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html#$controllerMap-detail">yii\base\Module::$controllerMap</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property, similar to<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-applications.html#controller-map">what you do in an application</a>.</p>
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Views in Modules<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="views-in-modules"></a></h3>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Views in a module should be put in the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">views</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>directory within the module's<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html#$basePath-detail">base path</a>. For views rendered by a controller in the module, they should be put under the directory<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">views/ControllerID</code>, where<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">ControllerID</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>refers to the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-controllers.html#routes">controller ID</a>. For example, if the controller class is<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">PostController</code>, the directory would be<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">views/post</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>within the module's<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html#$basePath-detail">base path</a>.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">A module can specify a<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-views.html#layouts">layout</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>that is applied to the views rendered by the module's controllers. The layout should be put in the<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">views/layouts</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>directory by default, and you should configure the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html#$layout-detail">yii\base\Module::$layout</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property to point to the layout name. If you do not configure the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">layout</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property, the application's layout will be used instead.</p>
<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 30px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Using Modules<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="using-modules"></a></h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">To use a module in an application, simply configure the application by listing the module in the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$modules-detail">modules</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property of the application. The following code in the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-applications.html#application-configurations">application configuration</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>uses the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">forum</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>module:</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'modules'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'forum'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'class'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'app\modules\forum\Module'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;...&nbsp;other&nbsp;configurations&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;module&nbsp;...<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />]</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">The<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#$modules-detail">modules</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property takes an array of module configurations. Each array key represents a<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><em style="box-sizing: border-box;">module ID</em><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>which uniquely identifies the module among all modules in the application, and the corresponding array value is a<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-concept-configurations.html">configuration</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>for creating the module.</p>
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Routes<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="routes"></a></h3>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Like accessing controllers in an application,<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-controllers.html#routes">routes</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>are used to address controllers in a module. A route for a controller within a module must begin with the module ID followed by the controller ID and action ID. For example, if an application uses a module named<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">forum</code>, then the route<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">forum/post/index</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>would represent the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">index</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>action of the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">post</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>controller in the module. If the route only contains the module ID, then the<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html#$defaultRoute-detail">yii\base\Module::$defaultRoute</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property, which defaults to<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">default</code>, will determine which controller/action should be used. This means a route<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">forum</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>would represent the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">default</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>controller in the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">forum</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>module.</p>
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Accessing Modules<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="accessing-modules"></a></h3>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Within a module, you may often need to get the instance of the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/guide-structure-modules.html#module-classes">module class</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>so that you can access the module ID, module parameters, module components, etc. You can do so by using the following statement:</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$module&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">MyModuleClass</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">::</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">getInstance</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">();</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">where<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">MyModuleClass</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>refers to the name of the module class that you are interested in. The<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">getInstance()</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>method will return the currently requested instance of the module class. If the module is not requested, the method will return null. Note that You do not want to manually create a new instance of the module class because it will be different from the one created by Yii in response to a request.</p>
<blockquote style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 14px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: #eeeeee; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;">Info: When developing a module, you should not assume the module will use a fixed ID. This is because a module can be associated with an arbitrary ID when used in an application or within another module. In order to get the module ID, you should use the above approach to get the module instance first, and then get the ID via<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">$module-&gt;id</code>.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">You may also access the instance of a module using the following approaches:</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;get&nbsp;the&nbsp;module&nbsp;whose&nbsp;ID&nbsp;is&nbsp;"forum"<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$module&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&nbsp;\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">Yii</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">::</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$app</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">-&gt;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">getModule</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">(</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'forum'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">);<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;get&nbsp;the&nbsp;module&nbsp;to&nbsp;which&nbsp;the&nbsp;currently&nbsp;requested&nbsp;controller&nbsp;belongs<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$module&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&nbsp;\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">Yii</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">::</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$app</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">-&gt;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">controller</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">-&gt;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">module</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">;</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">The first approach is only useful when you know the module ID, while the second approach is best used when you know about the controllers being requested.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Once getting hold of a module instance, you can access parameters or components registered with the module. For example,</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$maxPostCount&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$module</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">-&gt;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">params</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'maxPostCount'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">];</span></code></pre>
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Bootstrapping Modules<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="bootstrapping-modules"></a></h3>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Some modules may need to be run for every request. The<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-debug-module.html">debug</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>module is such an example. To do so, list the IDs of such modules in the<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-application.html#bootstrap()-detail">bootstrap</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property of the application.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">For example, the following application configuration makes sure the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">debug</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>module is always load:</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'bootstrap'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'debug'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'modules'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'debug'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'yii\debug\Module'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />]</span></code></pre>
<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 30px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Nested Modules<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="nested-modules"></a></h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Modules can be nested in unlimited levels. That is, a module can contain another module which can contain yet another module. We call the former<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><em style="box-sizing: border-box;">parent module</em><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>while the latter<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><em style="box-sizing: border-box;">child module</em>. Child modules must be declared in the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" href="http://www.yiiframework.com/doc-2.0/yii-base-module.html#$modules-detail">modules</a><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>property of their parent modules. For example,</p>
<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; display: block; padding: 9.5px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.42857143; color: #333333; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border-left-width: 5px; border-style: none none none solid; border-left-color: #e0e5ea; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: #f5faff;"><code class="language-php" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">namespace&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">app</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">modules</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">forum</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">;<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />class&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">Module&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">extends&nbsp;\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">yii</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">base</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">\</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">Module<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">{<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">init</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">()<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">parent</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">::</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">init</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">();<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">$this</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">-&gt;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0000bb;">modules&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'admin'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;[<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #ff8000;">//&nbsp;you&nbsp;should&nbsp;consider&nbsp;using&nbsp;a&nbsp;shorter&nbsp;namespace&nbsp;here!<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'class'&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">=&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #dd0000;">'app\modules\forum\modules\admin\Module'</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #007700;">,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;];<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />}</span></code></pre>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">For a controller within a nested module, its route should include the IDs of all its ancestor module. For example, the route<code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">forum/admin/dashboard/index</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>represents the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">index</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>action of the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">dashboard</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>controller in the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">admin</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>module which is a child module of the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; color: #c7254e; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; background-color: #f9f2f4;">forum</code><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>module.</p>
<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 30px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Best Practices<a style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #428bca; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" name="best-practices"></a></h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Modules are best used in large applications whose features can be divided into several groups, each consisting of a set of closely related features. Each such feature group can be developed as a module which is developed and maintained by a specific developer or team.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">Modules are also a good way of reusing code at the feature group level. Some commonly used features, such as user management, comment management, can all be developed in terms of modules so that they can be reused easily in future projects.</p>